{"tid":2041031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國宣布起訴中國通過電信公司幫朝鮮轉移巨資","createTime":"2020-05-29T03:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T05:05:50.000Z","uid":1241,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a32f0967603bce9ffedb9d8816801fd12806eeb","tid":2041031,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:34:09.000Z","msg":"美國司法部5月28日宣布對28名朝鮮公民和5名中國公民提起訴訟，指控他們通過一系列鏡像公司網絡，繞開了對朝鮮的核活動制裁令，轉移了超過25億美元，主要罪名涉及謀畫罪，違反國際緊急經濟權力法，銀行詐騙，和國際洗錢。<br />\n<br />\n根據這份起訴書，參與上述系列活動的鏡像公司約有250家，在泰國，利比亞，奧地利，俄羅斯，中國，科威特等國家境內，涉嫌通過國際銀行繞開對朝制裁，與朝鮮內部進行貨物貿易活動，幫助朝鮮獲得所需物資，同時獲利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200528-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E9%9B%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%B9%AB%E6%9C%9D%E9%AE%AE%E8%BD%89%E7%A7%BB%E5%B7%A8%E8%B3%87?ref=tw_i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20200528-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E%25E9%259B%25BB%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E6%259C%259D%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E8%25BD%2589%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E8%25B3%2587%3Fref%3Dtw_i&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33GlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=5b7ace7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200528-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E9%9B%BB%E4%BF%A1%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%B9%AB%E6%9C%9D%E9%AE%AE%E8%BD%89%E7%A7%BB%E5%B7%A8%E8%B3%87?ref=tw_i</a>"},{"pid":"1b3f2cc1103a669c1d3f3a0d9f469e690a2f384b","tid":2041031,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:35:26.000Z","msg":"陸續有嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde1d14054b182485e16517320e6fc2cf733ddf9","tid":2041031,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor